{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_05_04",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 05 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうしたんだ、すみれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong‚ Sumire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "元気ないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smrbro003.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、なんでもないよ、お兄ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's nothing‚ big brother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ……。俺の前でまで演技をするなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… Don't act in front of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すみれは聞き分けが良過ぎるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're too obedient‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "また学校で何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did something happen at school again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smrbro004.m4a",
      "text": "……お兄ちゃんには、なんですぐ分かっちゃうの？\n今のすみれのお芝居、ヘタっぴだった……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Big brother‚ how do you always know?\nWas Sumire's acting bad just now…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなことない。演技上手だって評判じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. You have a reputation for being a good actress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "俺がすみれの演技を見破れるのは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason I can see through your acting is――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.84,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smrbro005.m4a",
      "text": "れるのは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……すみれの、お兄ちゃんだからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Because I'm your brother‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなことより、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smrbro006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、あのね。お仕事で遠足に行けなくなっちゃって\nそれで、私、みんなの話に入れなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you see‚ I can't go on the school trip because of work‚\nand I… I can't join everyone's conversations…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遠足に行けばいいじゃないか。たまには仕事休めよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just go on the school trip. Take a break from work sometimes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんなら、俺が父さんか母さんに話して――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want‚ I'll talk to Dad or Mom――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smrbro007.m4a",
      "text": "ううん！　いいの！　私、お仕事好きだから！\nお兄ちゃんは気にしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! It's okay! I like my work!\nDon't worry about it‚ big brother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……すみれ、お前……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sumire‚ you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "（うん、今の演技は上手に出来た）\n（お兄ちゃんだって、気付いてない……はず）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Yes‚ that was good acting.)\n(Big brother didn't notice… I'm sure.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "（私は、お兄ちゃんが大好き）\n（お兄ちゃんが弾くピアノも、大好き）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I love my brother so much.)\n(I love his piano playing too.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "（いつか、お兄ちゃんは言ってた）\n（海外に留学して、本格的にピアノを習いたいって）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(He said once‚)\n(that he wanted to study piano abroad seriously.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、それには沢山のお金がかかる）\n（うちはお金持ちじゃない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But that requires a lot of money.)\n(Our family isn't wealthy.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "（だったら、私が、お仕事を頑張って）\n（お兄ちゃんの夢を叶えてあげたい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(So‚ if I work hard‚)\n(I want to make my brother's dream come true.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "（なのに――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But――)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 123.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 123.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……どうしたの？　すみれ\n今のターン遅かったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What's wrong‚ Sumire?\nYou were late on that turn just now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 128.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "――えっ？　あっ、ご、ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh? Oh‚ s-sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 131.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、全然練習に身が入ってないなぁ\n……まぁ、あんな話聞かされたら、無理もないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ you're not focused on practice at all.\n…Well‚ it's understandable after hearing that story‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 141.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……お家のこと、心配よね\nやっぱりまだ帰って来るべきじゃなかったかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm worried about your family.\nMaybe you shouldn't have come back yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 148.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい\n私、二人の足を引っ張っちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry.\nI'm holding you two back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 156.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないけど、もう一回、三人で山形行こか？\nうち、今のすみれちゃん見てるの辛いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true‚ but do you want us to go to Yamagata with you again?\nI hate seeing you like this‚ Sumire-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5689961477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 165.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私、お兄ちゃんに言われたの\nもう実家のことは気にするなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ my brother told me\nnot to worry about our family anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 172.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "私は、私の夢を追えって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He told me to chase my dream…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 177.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "お兄さんは、本当にピアニストになる夢を\n諦めてしまうの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is your brother really giving up\non his dream of becoming a pianist?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 181.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
